content: I've been taking a morning yoga class on Tuesdays and Thursdays, which forces me to wake up at 6:45 AM on those days. I've noticed that on those days, I tend to have more productive mornings and I'm more likely to fit in a lunchtime workout or a short walk during my break. I'm thinking of incorporating more protein into my breakfast to help me stay full until lunchtime. Do you think that would help?
